{
  "stem": "1530.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they made us stay in this little village somewhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to take care of there-- there was some animals, which they wanted to take away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to learn how to milk the animals--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And running at night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Worried they're going to get in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they weren't going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to us--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes and no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because to an Orthodox Jewish girl who's never had sex, the fear of that was horrendous.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And yet, we found some nice Russians, the younger ones, who understand-- understood and said, we'll stay with you tonight, or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We'll watch you, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's amazing, but there were some young people who kind of took us under their wing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was terribly frightening, terribly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the three of you were still together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Three of us together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we still didn't know what's going to happen to us, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because after a while, the Russians didn't have any more food.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, go, go, go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And everybody who was liberated, there were army-- American army men, from Israel, from India, the whole world was marching from over Silesia.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Two weeks we were marching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, somebody said, we're going to a place called [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oelsk. ?]",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it's O-E-L-S-K.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or just O-L-S-K.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there is a train, and it's going to take us somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no food anyway.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, you met people from all over that were prisoners in Germany, or working in Germany, and an army marching in this cold weather.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And two weeks of walking, we arrived in [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oelsk. ?] And--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think, in Upper Silesia, near [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Proschwitz, ?] or near somewhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It must have been, still, Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
